race.description: Janelle Puppa Real Estate Maiden Plate
race.comment: BASILICA (6) returns after a 5-and-a-half-month break and will be having her first run from the Freedman stable. She won her latest jumpout and looks ready to rumble. On top. ROSANGELA (13) has improved with two runs back from a spell, last time out finishing third at Traralgon over 1100m, just a length behind the winner. Expect her to be prominent early, and then to be still there at the business end of the race. EXCELS (8) debuted over 1000m at Moonee Valley and had an excuse when being beaten as the favourite. She is having her first run for the season, but has been burning up the training track, and only needs some luck from a wide draw to take this out. Follow your money. SPARTAN LASS (14) is a well-bred filly making her debut, and she has won her most recent jumpout. Watch the markets closely.
